descriptionHtml:
she is a lvl 1 High elf follower combat dual wield melee..She can be found at the banner mare in whiterun..She is in a simple Barkeep gown and is equipped with two iron swords.. so you may  give her anything  better and she won't stick her nose up at it




---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UPDATE

Updated both unp and CBBE both  are better compressed and  have their own skin and meshes.. niether now include my eyes conversion effecting player eyes.. However the file size will still be a bit big  as I included  the faceparts /textures and meshes needed for creating her..


Optional
I have  included  a conversion of human eyes so elves can use it..I believe this only  effects the players not npcs..I have included   eyes textures  with them but  I did not do the eyes textures ..If you do not want the  eyes textures just either 1.) only  install esp or 2.) over write the textures with the ones you preffer

eye texture were done by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/328241]pikkatze[/url]
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3424/?





--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                            
for her to dual wield sheathes
you need dual sheath redux for her  to show both weapon sheathes.. you might have to deactivate the npc in mcm menu but  reactivate should fix ..Unfortunatly  the  dual wield redux creator  refuses to answer his messages so I can't garentee  that  the dual wield sheathes  will  indeed function on her..But   you do not need the sheathes for her to actually wield the weapons  ..



if your using follower mods like Aft..then you might have to go into options  combat style  dual sword .. otherwise  atf will give her a bow upon first encounter in combat and remove her swords she comes with.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                                            Armoring

Outfit.. in atf or follower   mod  make sure you check to manage her outfit.

for cbbe version you need  armor compatible with CBBE curvy

for UNP -you need  armor compatible with UNP body.. Can use armor  tbbp(bounce) and  HDT if you want  as the body is TBBP compatible


 please if there is a grey face let me know i  will always see her as normal..I will never ask for money in any form donation or otherwise..If you really want to donate money donate it to this site ;)) so  modders   can continue to upload here

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

to uninstall
delete esp..make sure  anything aefaymi is deleted in textures and the meshes.. sometimes  you have to delete them when upgrading

if you want her to use your skin  copy the  textures from textures>>actors/ character >> female >> to the aefaymi >> body

be sure to copy and paste the file  under high elf as well.. though I think that fair skin texture is quite good for elves
